location.fullValue: WESLEY Plan, The Villas at Haywood Glen

data.description: Imagine you're home! Stunning, move-in ready home with 4 bedrooms, huge loft, and open floor plan.  New paint throughout and new carpet on stairs and 2nd floor. Impressive custom wainscoting, beautiful backyard for entertaining, and designer ready closets.  Soaking tub and separate shower in main suite that opens into the spacious main closet.  Don't miss this beautiful home in one of Knightdale's best neighborhoods with walking trails, community pool with wading area, and multiple playgrounds.
